randoop.field

Class InstanceField

  • Object
    • AccessibleField
      • InstanceField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class InstanceField
extends AccessibleField
    InstanceField represents an instance field of a class. This means that to be set, the field must be qualified by the object.
    See Also:
